subject: Excel not responding
description: Excel hangs or freezes when you launch it, or open an Excel workbook
resolution_notes: If you are on Windows 11 or Windows 10, choose Start > All apps > Windows System > Run. Type Excel /safe in the Run box, and then click OK.
resolution_notes_ITSM: Start Registry editor. To do this, press the Windows key + R to open a Run dialog box. Type regedit.exe and then press OK.

resolution_notes_ITSM: You can start Outlook in safe mode, disable your add-ins, and then try to open Outlook normally.

subject: cant log in to vpn
resolution_notes: check your network settings.Check if you are connected to internet.
resolution_notes_ITSM: Click the Windows icon in the bottom-left of the screen and type “Windows Defender Firewall” (without quotes). Now, select Allow an app or feature through Windows Defender Firewall in the list on the left. On the next screen, click Change settings and then Allow another app. Finally, locate your VPN app and click Add.

subject: unable to disable add ins on outlook
description: unable to disable add ins on outlook
resolution_notes: Open the Microsoft Outlook client.Select “File” > “Options“.Choose “Add-ins”.Uncheck the Add-ins you wish to turn off.
resolution_notes_ITSM: Open the Microsoft Outlook client.Select “File” > “Options“.Choose “Add-ins”.Uncheck the Add-ins you wish to turn off.

subject: Want to reset the password for outlook
description: hi I want to reset my outlook password.
